WEBVTT FILE:

00:00:00.850 --> 00:00:05.290
when you have to travel for the military, T D Y or T 80 for a time frame

00:00:05.290 --> 00:00:09.730
 usually are authorized by your command. You go in through DTs and

00:00:09.730 --> 00:00:14.170
 build your ticket. And sometimes if it's a plane or rental car and

00:00:14.170 --> 00:00:18.610
 all the different things you might need once that's approved from your

00:00:18.610 --> 00:00:23.050
 command, you go on your trip and you have to pay for the trip yourself,

00:00:23.050 --> 00:00:27.490
 at least initially. Whether it's through a government credit

00:00:27.490 --> 00:00:31.930
 card that you're issued as soon as you come back from that trip is your

00:00:31.930 --> 00:00:36.370
 responsibility to quickly liquidated, We think within five business

00:00:36.370 --> 00:00:40.810
 days, it's then approved by your command, and normally you get paid

00:00:40.810 --> 00:00:45.250
 within 72 hours of that.

